OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fshowers becoming confined to eastern
OL,7,Fareas, with it turning drier for a
OL,8,Ftime overnight with clear skies.
OL,9,FHowever, low cloud and rain arrives in
OL,10,Fthe west through the early hours.
OL,11,FTurning milder in the west, chilly
OL,12,Felsewhere.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FA wet and rather windy day
OL,15,Fas rain spreads across east, turning
OL,16,Flocally heavy at times, but easing
OL,17,Flater. Feeling muggy under widespread
OL,18,Fcloud cover. Turning drier by the
OL,19,Fevening.
